1. Jalen Tools:
---------------

The Jalen Tools are a number of tools to process the information provided by Jalen agent.
Jalen Tools have the following tools:
- Aggregation Tool: a tool that process the files generated by Jalen agent and provide a list of the power consumption of methods, classes and packages.

Version: 0.0.1

Last update : 23/03/2012 (23 March 2012)


2. Requirements:
----------------

This prototype requires the following libraries and tools:
- Maven2 to compile and run the prototype


3. Usage:
---------

To build and compile all modules:
-> mvn clean package

To run the tools:
-> mvn exec:java -Dexec.args="/Path/to/dumpData.csv type"
where type is the format type of the power values. Type can either be watt or per (percentage).

For example:
-> mvn exec:java -Dexec.args="/Path/to/dumpData.csv per"
-> mvn exec:java -Dexec.args="/Path/to/dumpData.csv watt"